title: Winterport Dragway continues cool, hot action Oct. 11
text:
Winterport Dragway continues cool, hot action Oct. 11 By Staff | Oct 12, 2015 
Winterport — Fall racing continued at a fast pace on Sunday, Oct. 11 at Winterport Dragway. 
The individual results were: 
Super Pro/ Pro — 1, Justin Reynolds, Albion; and 2, Rick Hunnewell, Ellsworth. 
Super Pro Eliminator — 1, Rick Hunnewell, Ellsworth; and 2, Willy Larrabee, Stockton Springs. Semifinalists: Paul Henckel, Old Orchard Beach; and Bob Cousins, Brewer. 
Pro Eliminator — 1, Justin Reynolds, Albion; and 2, John Sloan, Topsham. Semifinalists: Terry Sawyer, Hancock; and Gage Reynolds, Old Town. 
Street Eliminator — 1, Randy Herrick, Stockton Springs; and 2, Dan Poirier, Minot. Semifinalist: Alyssa Walcott, Bernard. 
Bikes and Sleds — 1, Frank John, Brooklin; and 2, Kelsey Mushero, Fairfield. Semifinalist: Everett Beers, West Tremont. 
Junior Dragster — 1, Danielle Fusco, Turner; and 2, Jaylee Soucy, Monmouth. Semifinalist: Jonathan Condon, Chelsea. 
Darling's Ford Gamblers — 1, Chip Taylor, Hancock; and 2, Rick Hunnewell, Ellsworth, Semifinalist: Bob Cousins, Brewer. Courier Publications' sports staff can be reached by email at sports@villagesoup.com or by phone at 594-4401.
